https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/halsey@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/halsey">哈尔西</a>终于宣布了他们的新专辑“The Great Impersonator”——了解更多信息如下。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><b>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/halsey-if-i-cant-have-love-i-want-power-review-3030014">哈尔西——“如果我不能拥有爱，我想要权力”评论：无尽引人注目的艺术陈述</a><br /></b></li></ul><p>昨晚（8 月 27 日），这位创作型歌手（代称“她/他们”）在社交媒体上分享了这张专辑的预告片，该专辑被描述为“一张忏悔概念专辑”。</p><p>他们尚未宣布专辑的发行日期，也没有分享唱片的曲目列表或功能列表。然而，在预告片视频中，哈尔西开玩笑说，这张专辑将让他们穿越时空，探索过去几十年的音乐风格。 </p><figure id="attachment_3502844" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3502844" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3502844" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Halsey-posing.jpg" alt="哈尔西于 2023 年 3 月 12 日抵达加利福尼亚州比佛利山庄沃利斯·安纳伯格表演艺术中心举办的由拉迪卡·琼斯主持的《名利场》奥斯卡派对。图片来源：Robert Smith/Patrick McMullan via Getty" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Halsey-posing.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Halsey-posing-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Halsey-posing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Halsey-posing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Halsey-posing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Halsey-posing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3502844" class="wp-caption-text">哈尔西于 2023 年 3 月 12 日抵达加利福尼亚州比佛利山庄沃利斯·安纳伯格表演艺术中心举办的由拉迪卡·琼斯主持的《名利场》奥斯卡派对。图片来源：Robert Smith/Patrick McMullan via Getty</figcaption></figure><p>他们在预告片中反思自己<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/halsey-shares-health-update-following-the-release-of-new-song-the-end-3762993">被诊断出患有狼疮和一种罕见的 T 细胞淋巴增殖性疾病后</a>的生活：“当你患上这样的病时，你会开始思考一切可能会有所不同。”</p><p>他们继续说道：“如果我在 2000 年代初出道怎么办？九十年代？八十年代？七十年代？每次我还是哈尔西吗？在每个时间线中，我还会生病吗？我要当妈妈了吗？”</p><p>请观看下面哈尔西的《伟大的模仿者》的预告片。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/C_LecrlRD7B/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66.113 C549.9,66.113 557.115,58.899 557.115,50 C557.115,41.1 549.9,33.886 541,33.886 M565.378,62.101 C565.244,65.022 564.756,66.606 564.346,67.663